OL,3,CNine men charged in child sexual
OL,4,Cexploitation investigation
OL,6,FNine men have appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with 40 historical child
OL,8,Fsexual exploitation offences.
OL,10,FThe men, aged 54 to 76, were arrested
OL,11,Fby detectives from Gwent Police
OL,12,Fearlier in July.
OL,14,FThe investigation was part of
OL,15,FOperation Oak, which looked into
OL,16,Freports of sexual abuse made by women
OL,17,Fwho were children at the time of the
OL,18,Falleged offences between 1985 and 1996.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
