OL,3,CNine men charged in child sexual
OL,4,Cexploitation investigation
OL,6,FThe defendants, who are all British
OL,7,Fcitizens, appeared before Newport
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court for a first hearing
OL,9,Fon Friday (24 July) , and spoke only
OL,10,Fto confirm their names, dates of birth
OL,11,Fand addresses.
OL,13,FNone of them were asked to enter a
OL,14,Fplea during the short hearing. They
OL,15,Fare:
OL,17,FMurad Ali, 57, from Swansea.
OL,19,FSheikh Mohammed Tahir Ullah, 73, from
OL,20,FNewport.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
