OL,3,CNine men charged in child sexual
OL,4,Cexploitation investigation
OL,6,FAminur Rahman Chowdhury, 58, of
OL,7,FTottenham, north London.
OL,9,FAfter three brief hearings on Friday,
OL,10,Fthe eight men were released on
OL,11,Fconditional bail. They will next
OL,12,Fappear at Cardiff Crown Court on
OL,13,FAugust 21.
